{"tid":2057758,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警車無響號衝燈撞人 警控危駕","createTime":"2020-06-09T15:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T15:35:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"257a44eb6cf909faa6023e68eaa6b5c7c4adfc85","tid":2057758,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200609/HF7B4YJD5BATT5VFC43B3XLUTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200609%2FHF7B4YJD5BATT5VFC43B3XLUTI%2F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelnjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=f11e6cc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200609%2FHF7B4YJD5BATT5VFC43B3XLUTI%2F&h=56f3405a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200609/HF7B4YJD5BATT5VFC43B3XLUTI/</a><br />\n<br />\n警車無響號衝燈撞人 警控危駕<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警員深夜駕警車前往處理一宗暈倒事故時，在秀茂坪衝紅燈撞傷一名居於秀茂坪紀律部隊宿舍的夜歸婦，婦人被撞致頭骨骨折，一度留醫深切治療部。涉事警員承認不小心駕駛，但否認危險駕駛引致他人身體受嚴重傷害罪昨受審。辯方指警員心急救人，觀察路面後發現無人才無視交通燈，當時有着警示燈，但承認無響警號。案件今裁決。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OMETNEGGLSPS4JO45Q7ZIHSD3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOMETNEGGLSPS4JO45Q7ZIHSD3U.jpg&h=e21d8df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告陳家傑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯稱車頭燈影響視線<br />\n<br />\n案發去年3月8日，被告陳家傑（47歲）在秀茂坪康寧道與振華道交界撞倒女子蔣一平（37歲）。蔣供稱當晚約11時10分過馬路，行人過路燈是綠燈，及後遭撞倒並不省人事。辯方盤<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n過路燈的綠燈已在閃爍，但蔣仍心急過路，她亦不記得。<br />\n<br />\n被告表證成立，不自辯亦不傳召證人。他在警誡下稱起初想在路口右轉，但考<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n視線因而受阻，難察覺事主。辯方強調，被告有20多年駕駛經驗，從無交通定罪紀錄，案發時無超速，且撞倒事主前一刻已煞車，並非無留意路面情況。辯方直言被告只是缺乏專注，而非遠遜於一名及格和謹慎駕駛者，不構成危險駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n至於沒響警號，辯方解釋，僅着警示燈已足夠，且警隊多年來均容許警員在晚<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n無法察覺警車駛至；辯方回應指法例並無規定響警號。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC1545/19<br />\n■記者楊思雅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TNFBBYSPQ3RK534DCMCMQ775BQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTNFBBYSPQ3RK534DCMCMQ775BQ.jpg&h=186f394e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傷者蔣一平"},{"pid":"3be0575d7da3057e08411f59d0a7ae04c58c5690","tid":2057758,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗？"},{"pid":"4d9e8f761484fd03e413df520f25af899c61c313","tid":2057758,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:35:02.000Z","msg":"佢最白痴就係唔響號<br />\n屌佢老味平時啲狗一見紅燈就即刻響架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}